        { "region": "China / Tibet", "description": "China's infrastructure build-up in Tibet — roads, railways, military installations directly across from Arunachal Pradesh — compresses India's strategic response time. The BRO (Border Roads Organisation)'s accelerated construction post-2020 is India's counter. Northeast India is where the India-China strategic competition is most physically visible on the ground." }
